Flicker/Phoenix/Skyblaze::

"Understood, Blackstorm.  I'll check this out myself."  Flicker moves 
through the halls and comes across Starstorm and company.  "Who's 
this?" he asks, indicating Skyblaze.

"This is Skyblaze; he's ... my father," Phoenix explains, a bit 
embarrassed.

Flicker hides his surprise.  "The three of you come with me.  There's 
a Maximal in our territory and I want to find out why."  He heads off 
down the corridor toward the exit; Phoenix quickly catches up to him.

Skyblaze looks at Starstorm.  "Shall we go?"
